subject account of anti armenian human right violat in azerbaijan account of anti armenian human right violat in azerbaijan prelud to current event in nagorno karabakh i said that on februari when those peopl were stream down our street thei were shout long live turkei and glori to turkei and dure the trial i said to that ismailov what doe that mean glori to turkei i still don t understand what turkei ha to do with thi we live in the soviet union that turkei told you to or is go to help you kill armenian i still don t understand why glori to turkei i ask that question twice and got no answer no on answer me deposit of emma setrakovna sargisian born cook sumgait emerg hospit resid at build apart block sumgait azerbaijan to thi dai i can t understand why my husband an older man wa kill what wa he kill for he hadn t hurt anyon hadn t said ani word he oughtn t have why did thei kill him i want to find out from here from there from the govern why my husband wa kill on the th when i return from work it wa a saturdai my son wa at home he doesn t work i went straight to the kitchen and he call me mamma is there a soccer game there were shout from lenin street that s where we live i sai i don t know igor i haven t turn on the tv he look again and said mamma what s go on in the courtyard i look and see so mani peopl it s aw march march there ar hundr thousand you can t even tell how mani there ar thei re shout down with the armenian kill the armenian tear the armenian to piec my god why is that happen what for i had known noth at that point we live togeth well in friendship and suddenli someth like thi it wa complet unexpect and thei were shout long live turkei and thei had flag and thei were shout there wa a man walk in front well dress he s around or in a grai raincoat he is walk and sai someth i can t make it out through the vent window he is walk and sai someth and the children behind him ar shout tear the armenian to piec and down with the armenian thei shout it again and then shout hurrah the peopl stream without end thei were walk in group and in the group i saw that there were women too i sai my god there ar women there too and my son sai those aren t women mamma those ar bad women well we didn t look a long time thei were walk and shout and i wa afraid i simpli couldn t sit still i went out onto the balconi and my azerbaijani neighbor is on the other balconi and i sai khalida what s go on what happen she sai emma i don t know i don t know i don t know what happen well she wa quit frighten too thei had these white stick each second or third on had a white rod thei re wave the rod abov their head as thei walk and the on who s out front like a leader he ha a white stick too well mayb it wa an armatur shaft but what i saw wa white i don t know my husband got home or minut later he come home and i sai oh dear i m frighten thei re go to kill us i bet and he sai what ar you afraid of thei re just children i sai everyth that happen come from children there had been and year kid from the technic and vocat school don t fear he said it s noth noth all that bad he didn t eat he just lai on the sofa and just then on televis thei broadcast that two azerbaijani had been kill in karabakh near askeran when i heard that i couldn t settl down at all i kept walk here and there and i said thei re go to kill us the azerbaijani ar go to kill us and he sai don t be afraid then we heard from the central squar there ar women shout near near the stage well thei re shout differ thing and you couldn t hear everi well i sai you speak azerbaijani well listen to what thei re sai he sai close the window and go to bed there s noth happen there he listen a bit and then close the window and went to bed and told us come on go to sleep it s noth sleep what did he mean sleep my son and i stood at the window until two in the morn watch well he s sick and all of thi wa affect him i sai igor you go to bed i m go to go to bed in a minut too he went and i sat at the window until three and then went to bed thing had calm down slightli the th sundai wa my dai off my husband got up and said come on emma get up i sai todai s my dai off let me rest he sai aren t you go to make me some tea well i felt startl and got up and said where ar you go he sai i m go out i have to i sai can you realli go outsid on a dai like todai don t go out for god s sake you never listen to me i know and you re not go to listen to me now but at least don t take the car out of the garag go without the car and he sai come on close the door and then on the staircas he mutter someth i couldn t make it out he probabl said coward or someth i close the door and he left and i start clean pick thing up around the hous everyth seem quiet until on o clock in the after noon but at the bu station my neighbor told me car were burn i said khalida wa it our car she sai no no emma don t be afraid thei were govern car and zhiguli our car is a gaz volga and i wait it wa four o clock five o clock and when he wasn t home at seven i said oh thei ve kill shagen tire ar burn in town there s black smoke in town and i m afraid i m stand on the balconi and i m all my whole bodi is shake my god thei ve probabl kill him so basic i wait like that until ten o clock and he still hadn t come home and i m afraid to go out at ten o clock i look out across from our build is a build with a bookstor and from upstair from the second floor everyth is be thrown outsid i m look out of on window and igor is look out of the other and i don t want him to see thi and he as it turn out doesn t want me to see it we want to hide it from on anoth i join him mamma he sai look what thei re do over there thei were burn everyth and there were polic stand there or of them mayb twenti policemen stand on the side and the crowd is on the other side and two or three peopl ar throw everyth down from the balconi and on of the on on the balconi is shout what ar you stand there for burn it when thei threw the televis wow it wa like a bomb our neighbor on the third floor came out on her balconi and shout why ar you do that why ar you burn those thing those peopl save with such difficulti to bui those thing for their home why ar you burn them and from the courtyard thei yell at her go insid go insid instead why don t you tell us if thei ar ani of them in your build or not thei meant armenian but thei didn t sai armenian thei said of them she sai no no no none then she ran downstair to our place and sai emma emma you have to leav i sai thei ve kill shagen anywai what do we have to live for it won t be live for me without shagen let them kill us too she insist sai emma get out of here go to khalida s and give me the kei when thei come i ll sai that it s my daughter s apart that thei re off visit someon i gave her the kei and went to the neighbor s but i couldn t endur it i sai igor you stai here i m go to go downstair and see mayb papa s papa s there meanwhil thei were kill the two brother alik and valeri albert and valeri avanesian see the account of rima avanesian and alvina baluian in the courtyard there is a crowd near the build thei re shout howl and i didn t think that thei were kill at the time alik and valeri live in the corner hous across from our when i went out into the courtyard i saw an azerbaijani our neighbor a young man about year old i sai madar uncl shagen s gone let s go see mayb he s dead in the garag or near the garag let s at least bring the corps into the hous he shout aunt emma where do you think you re go go back into the hous i ll look for him i sai someth will happen to you too becaus of me no madar i m come too well he wouldn t let me go all the same he sai you stai here with us i m go look he went and look and came back and said aunt emma there s no on there the garag is close madar went off again and then return and said aunt emma thei re alreadi kill alik and valeri s there wheez madar want to go up to him but those scoundrel said don t go near him or we ll put you next to him he got scare he s young and came back and said i m go to go call mayb an ambul will come at least to take alik mayb he ll live thei grew up togeth in our courtyard thei knew each other well thei had alwai been on good term he went to call but not a singl telephon work thei had all been shut off he call and call and call and call noth i went upstair to the neighbor s igor sai two polic car drove up over there their headlight ar on but thei re not touch them thei ar still ly where thei were thei re still ly there we watch out the window until four o clock and then went downstair to our apart i didn t take my cloth off i lai on the couch so as not to go to bed and at six o clock in the morn i got up and said igor you stai here at home don t go out don t go anywher i m go to look i have to find papa dead or aliv let me go i ve got the kei from work at six o clock i went to the emerg hospit the head doctor and anoth doctor open the door to the morgu i run up to them and sai doctor is shagen there he sai what do you mean why should shagen be here i want to go in but he wouldn t let me there were onli four peopl in there thei said well thei must have been aw becaus thei didn t let me in thei said shagen s not here he s aliv somewher he ll come back it s alreadi seven o clock in the morn i look and there is a panel truck with three policemen some of our peopl from the hospit were there with them i sai sara baji sister sara term of endear go look thei ve probabl brought shagen i said it shout it and she went and came back and sai no emma he ha tan shoe on it s a younger person now shagen just happen to have tan shoe light tan thei were alreadi old when thei said it like that i guess immedi i went and said doctor thei ve brought shagen in dead he sai why ar you carri on like that dead dead he s aliv but then he went all the same and when he came back the look on hi face wa i could tell immedi that he wa dead thei knew on anoth well shagen had work for him a long time i sai doctor is it shagen he sai no emma it s not he it s somebodi els entir i sai doctor why ar you deceiv me i ll find out all the same anywai if not todai then tomorrow and he said i scream right there in the offic he sai emma go go calm down a littl anoth on of our colleagu said that the doctor had said it wa shagen but in hideou condit thei tri to calm me down sai it wasn t shagen a few minut later anoth colleagu come in and sai oh poor emma when she said it like that there wa no hope left that dai wa aw thei were endlessli bring in dead and injur peopl at night someon took me home i said igor papa s been kill on the morn of the st i left igor at home again and went to the hospit i had to buri him somehow do someth i look and see that the hospit is surround by soldier thei ar wear dark cloth hei citizen where ar you go i sai i work here and from insid someon shout ye ye that s our cook let her in i went right to the head doctor s offic and there is a person from the citi health depart there he us to work with us at the hospit he sai emma shagen s been taken to baku in the night thei took the wound and the dead all of them to baku i sai doctor how will i buri him he sai we re take care of all that don t you worri we ll do everyth we ll tell you about it where did you spend the night i sai i wa at home he sai what do you mean you were at home you were at home alon i sai no igor wa there too he sai you can t stai home we re get an ambul right now wait just on second the head doctor is come we re arrang an ambul right now you put on a lab coat and take on for igor you go and bring igor here like a patient and you ll stai here and we ll se later what to do next hi last name is kagramanov the head doctor s name is izyat jamalogli sadukhov the ambul arriv and i went home and got igor thei admit him as a patient thei gave us a privat room an isol room we stai in the hospit until the th some polic car came and thei said emma let s go and the women our colleagu then thei saw the polic car becam anxiou and said where ar you take her i sai thei re go to kill me too and the investig sai why ar you sai that we re go to make a posit identif we went to baku and thei took me into the morgu i still can t rememb what hospit it wa the investig sai let s go we need to be certain mayb it s not shagen and when i saw the casket ly on top of on anoth i went out of my mind i sai i can t look no the investig sai ar there ani identifi mark i sai let me see the cloth or the shoe or even a sock i ll recogn them he sai isn t thei re anyth on hi bodi i sai he ha seven gold teeth and hi finger he onli ha half of on of hi finger shagen wa a carpent he had been injur at work thei brought on of the sleev of the shirt and sweater he wa wear thei brought them and thei were all burn when i saw them i shout oh thei burn him i shout i don t know i fell down or mayb i sat down i don t rememb and that investig sai well fine fine sinc we ve identifi that these ar hi cloth and sinc hi teeth sinc he ha seven gold teeth on the th thei told me emma it s time to buri shagen now i cri how how can i buri shagen when i have onli on son and he s sick i should inform hi rel he ha three sister i can t do it by myself thei sai ok you know the situat how will thei get here from karabagh how will thei get here from yerevan there s no transport it s imposs he wa kill on februari and i buri him on march we buri him in sumgait thei ask me where do you want to buri him i said i want to buri him in karabagh where we were born let me buri him in karabagh i m shout and the head of the burial offic i guess sai do you know what it mean take him to karabagh it mean arson i sai what do you mean arson don t thei know what s go on in karabagh the whole world know that thei kill them and i want to take him to karabagh i don t have anyon anymor i beg i plead i griev i even got down on my knee he sai let s buri him here now and in three month in six month a year if it calm down i ll help you move him to karabagh our trial wa the first in sumgait it wa conclud on mai at the investig the murder tale ismailov told how it all happen but then at the trial he tri to wriggl he tri to soften hi crime then thei brought a videotap record i guess and plai it and said ismailov look is that you he sai ye well look here you re describ everyth as it wa on the scene of the crime right he sai ye and now you re tell it differ he sai well mayb i forgot like that the wit and that crimin creep himself said that when the car wa go along mir street there wa a crowd of about peopl shagen had a volga gaz the peopl surround hi car and all of them were involv on of them wa thi ismailov gui thi tale thei it s unclear who start pull shagen out of the car well on sai from the left side of the car anoth sai from the right side thei pull off hi sport jacket he had a jacket on well thei ask him what s your nation he sai armenian well thei sai from the crowd thei shout if he s an armenian kill him kill him thei start beat him thei broke seven of hi rib and hi heart i don t know thei did someth there too it s too aw to tell about anywai thei sai thi tale gui he had an armatur shaft he sai i pick it up it wa ly near a bush that s where i got it he said he pick it up but the wit sai that he had alreadi had it he said i hit him twice he said onc or twice on the head with that rod and he said that when he start to beat him shagen wa sit on the ground and when he hit him he fell over he said i left right nearbi thei were burn thing or someth in an apart kill someon he sai and i came back to look is that shagen aliv or not i said you want to finish him right and if he wa still aliv you came back to hit him again he went back and look and he wa alreadi dead after that that bastard tale said after that i went home i said you you littl snake i said ar you a thief and a murder shagen had had monei in hi jacket and a watch on hi wrist thei were taken he sai he didn t take them when thei overturn and burn the car that tale wa no longer there it wa other peopl who did that who it wa who turn over the car and who burn it that hasn t been clarifi as yet i told the investig how can you have the trial when you don t know who burn the car he said someth but i didn t get what he wa sai but i said you still haven t straighten everyth out i think that s unjust when thei burn the car he wa ly next to it and the fire spread to him in the death certif it sai that he had third degre burn over percent of hi bodi and i ask again why wa he kill my husband wa a carpent he wa a good craftsman he knew how to do everyth he even fix hi own car with hi own hand we have three children three son onli igor wa with me at the time the older on wa in pyatigorsk and the younger on is serv in the armi and now thei re fatherless i couldn t sit all the wai through it when the procur read up to year depriv of freedom i just i went out of my mind i didn t know what to do with myself i said how can that be you i said you ar sai that it wa intent murder and the sentenc is year depriv of freedom i scream i had my mind i said let me at that creep with my bare hand i ll a rel restrain me and there were all those militari peopl there i lest i said thi isn t a soviet trial thi is unjust that s what i shout l said it and left i said that on februari when those peopl were stream down our street thei were shout long live turkei and glori to turkei and dure the trial i said to that ismailov what doe that mean glori to turkei i still don t understand what turkei ha to do with thi we live in the soviet union that turkei told you to or is go to help you kill armenian i still don t understand why glori to turkei i ask that question twice and got no answer no on answer me mai yerevan refer the sumgait tragedi pogrom against armenian in soviet azerbaijan volum i eyewit account edit by samuel shahmuradian forward by yelena bonner publish by aristid d caratza ny page david davidian dbd urartu sdpa org how do we explain turkish troop on s d p a center for region studi the armenian border when we can t p o box even explain cambridg ma turkish mp march 